# Template and HTMX Patterns

## Rendering model

- full page routes render shells
- HTMX fetches component fragments into page targets
- API handlers should return components for HTML mode and plain data for JSON mode

## Polling behavior

Keep visibility-aware polling behavior

- poll every 10s while tab is visible
- poll every 60s while tab is hidden

Do not switch to websocket-first behavior unless explicitly requested

## Error handling pattern

- use server-rendered error fragment `templates/components/error.html`
- keep `htmx-config` response handling set to swap on 4xx and 5xx so errors render in place

## UI language

- status labels should stay consistent with current model
    - `Operational`
    - `Issues Detected`
